[{"id":259617,"type":2,"name":"劲爆战士","name_cn":"劲爆战士","summary":"《劲爆战士》是吴建荣出品的国产动画片，现已有三部。\r\n该动画以陀螺技艺大赛为叙述核心，设计了悬念迭起、扣人心弦的善恶势力对抗的故事，具有较强的情节性和观赏性。\r\n陀螺界一直有一个传说：曾经有七个人，各自拥有寄居着最强大圣兽的劲爆陀螺。他们把巨大的宝藏埋在无人知晓的海岛上，并且约定只有七个人同时把他们的劲爆陀螺摆成北斗七星阵，才能够开启宝藏。然而其中一人（巴斯）为了独吞宝藏，一直在暗地里不择手段的集圣兽陀螺。\r\n以劲爆战队的云晓虎、摩多、海力布、阿豹和林飞为主，围绕基因块开启了一场争夺战。劲爆战队为保护圣兽界，逐渐为成为超时空劲爆战士而努力。\r\n劲爆战队再次把巴斯封印在黑暗基地里。由于进入了梦境城市造成劲爆战队3个人（除摩多外）失忆了，在林飞的帮助下恢复了记忆。天阳天机等五人被巴斯利用，后来才醒悟过来。最终，劲爆战队战胜了巴斯，让F市重现光明。","date":"2008-09-01","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/97/b2/259617_VytT9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/97/b2/259617_VytT9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/97/b2/259617_VytT9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/97/b2/259617_VytT9.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/97/b2/259617_VytT9.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":6038,"total":61,"score":5.8,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":2,"5":21,"6":24,"7":9,"8":4,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"国产","count":27},{"name":"童年","count":19},{"name":"TV","count":15},{"name":"2008","count":9},{"name":"陀螺","count":6},{"name":"原创","count":3},{"name":"中国","count":3},{"name":"动画","count":2},{"name":"战斗","count":2},{"name":"⊘中国","count":2},{"name":"冒险","count":2}],"eps":39,"collection":{"wish":5,"collect":136,"doing":2,"on_hold":6,"dropped":14}},{"id":308270,"type":2,"name":"Martha Speaks","name_cn":"玛莎说话啦","summary":"The series revolves around a talking dog named Martha (voiced by Tabitha St. Germain), who is owned by 10-year-old Helen Lorraine (known in the books as Helen Finney). Whenever Helen feeds Martha alphabet soup, the noodle letters somehow travel to her brain instead of her stomach, giving her the ability to speak human words. The show takes place in the fictional town of Wagstaff City, likely referring to Flagstaff, Arizona[8] or even a fictionalized version of Flagstaff, Maine.","date":"2008-09-01","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/7b/3d/308270_Tf0pG.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/